By now you might have heard about how Meryl Streep won the internet after her provocative and emotional speech as she accepted the Cecil B DeMille lifetime achievement award at the 74th annual Golden Globe awards on Sunday evening.&nbsp; While arguably the best actress alive definitely stole the show during the 74th formulaic display of back pats and zealous thank yous, there were at least a dozen moments worth replaying.The 2017 Golden Globe awards will be re-screened tonight on M-Net channel 101 at 8.30pm